title: WIPO Member States Approve Organization’s 2016/17 Program and Budget (WIPO - World Intellectual Property Organization) ...
text: ( Source : WIPO - World Intellectual Property Organization ) Geneva , October 15 , 2015 PR/2015/783 Capping ten days of deliberations, WIPO member states approved the Organization 's Program and Budget for the two-year period beginning in 2016
